{"tid":186930,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"俠客風雲傳前傳","createTime":"2017-04-04T14:28:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T21:04:11.000Z","uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8030449971c9e54c45960dd1c337a8d9f12b0ab8","tid":186930,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:28:12.000Z","msg":"岩岩打爆機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好想玩落去<br />\n屌你閻羅個part無啦啦就死撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲諗住有排講<br />\n大師兄又唔同塔亞一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n天機老人原來係郭破虜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔怪得咁撚好抽 <br />\n好想佢出埋無暇子個代人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個故事應該好正<br />\n<br />\n岩先睇見話暑期前出鄷都DLC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n會唔會有孟婆比歐陽笑強姦睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 孟婆好撚正"},{"pid":"5a006eb4564639820fba545daaaaa577af5ac976","tid":186930,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:33:05.000Z","msg":"無人玩武俠game嫁咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f72e7255f6f1a266807bf8abe61bd6d6aa647f4f","tid":186930,"uid":103318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:33:07.000Z","msg":"想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93078d1074970e86409a22acbba5ef4d05e6b50e","tid":186930,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-04T14:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無玩前傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46890187bc447b350c8a504c2679d95787655043","tid":186930,"uid":8504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201